  "texts": [
    "These tools could be integrated into interactive assessments, e.g., games or picture tasks with recorded responses, enabling preliminary analyses of speech sound production, fluency, voice, and language.",
    "Such tools may generate draft reports and referrals for SLPs and other healthcare professionals.",
    "Such screening tasks will be supported by vision-based monitoring systems and fine-tuned SLMs capable of assessing risk and supporting decision-making.",
    "Additionally, commercial wearable devices that record speech and environmental context are already available.",
    "For instance, both Google and Meta offer smart glasses that can capture voice and video."
